        "body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every material we use is chosen for its natural beauty and authenticity. We don't hide imperfections — we celebrate them. Our handmade gemstone and pearl bracelets begin with materials sourced from specific regions around the world — freshwater pearls from China's high-standard farms, amethyst from Brazil's volcanic basalt deposits, agate from India and Madagascar. Each material is selected by hand in our California studio before it ever becomes a piece of jewelry.</p>",
